title: Demon Investigation Corporation: A D.I.C paranormal story - Round two
description: Jorge Sanderson is still working hard for D.I.C. Again, not like that! The Demon Investigation Corporation are the team you send in when the fairy tale creatures stop playing by the rules, and Jorge is on the front line despite being three months pregnant... And if being a mama-to-be isn't hard enough, a mysterious asshole has placed a tempting reward on Jorge's head. Now that the paranormal freaks are coming for her in force, hormones and giving birth are the least of her worries... With seemingly the entire supernatural community scrambling to kill her, Jorge will have to watch her back if she wants to live long enough to see her maternity leave.
author: Lorraine Agent
